'''''Bloodie''''' is a 1998 Czech video game for [[DOS]].
==Production== The game began life as a demo program and variation of the popular title [[Boovie]]<ref name="idnes.cz">{{cite web|url=https://plnehry.idnes.cz/bloodie-krvavy-bratricek-boovie-daa-/Clanek.aspx?c=A010311_093006_bw-plneHry-akcni_bw|title=Bloodie - krvavý bratříček Boovie|date=12 March 2001|website=iDNES.cz}}</ref>, and it uses the same graphics engine as the other game.<ref name="auto">{{cite web|url=https://doupe.zive.cz/clanek/bloodie--zachran-si-sveho-boovieho|title=Bloodie – zachraň si svého Boovieho|first=Michal|last=Acler|publisher=}}</ref> The game is similar to the [[Moorhuhn]] series.<ref name="auto"/>
==Critical reception== Bonusweb.cz felt the game was great and entertaining as few games are.<ref name="idnes.cz"/> Doupe.cz felt the graphics and music were decent and held up in the 2010s.<ref name="auto"/>
